         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">9/1/96 ¶  ¶ As you were so successful with the cultivation of the Mesembrianthemum edule, dear Miss Henley, may I ask, whether your plants happen to be in fruit. In that case I should be obliged for s...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">96.01.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Maria Henley</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M32a, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">9/1/96</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As you were so successful with the cultivation of the Mesembrianthemum edule, dear Miss Henley, may I ask, whether your plants happen to be in fruit. In that case I should be obliged for some of them or for the seeds taken out (the pulp not entirely removed) as it affords nutriment to the young seedling-plant.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to M. Henley, 15 January 1896.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With best New-years wishes to your worthy Parents and yourself.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
